cast.overview: Megan is an all-American girl. A cheerleader. She has a boyfriend. But Megan doesn't like kissing her boyfriend very much. And she's pretty touchy with her cheerleader friends. Her conservative parents worry that she must be a lesbian and send her off to "sexual redirection" school, where she must, with other lesbians and gays learn how to be straight.
cast.title: But I'm a Cheerleader

details.biography: Rachelle Diane Carson-Begley is an American actress and producer. She has been married to actor Ed Begley Jr. since August 23, 2000, and they have one child.
details.name: Rachelle Carson-Begley
